title: Undekhi
overview: Show depicts the two aspects of the society - the power-drunk influential people who think they can get away with anything and the oppressed, subjected to years of torture, who finally decide to bring themselves to justice

tv.episodeOverview: Teji’s lying and scheming catches up to her as she desperately tries to keep her world from unravelling. Meanwhile, Rinku and Daman discover the betrayal of a trusted ally and are hell bent on revenge, while Papaji is plagued by the ghosts of his past.
